    "description": [
      "Wind whips the highland ridge overlooking the black beaches verging on the steel-colored waters of the Frostmain.  Great icebergs breach out of the waters, some the size of cities, the remnants of glaciers that have finished their long migration to the sea.  The cries of seabirds fill the air and the scent of brine is on every cutting breeze."
